<tmc-service-paragraph><pub id="RM25T0E"><servcat id="_51"><name>Engine / Hybrid System</name><section id="_057930"><name>CRUISE CONTROL</name><ttl id="_0287962"><name>CRUISE CONTROL SYSTEM</name><para id="RM100000000ZP8M" category="C"><dtccode>P0503</dtccode><dtcname>Vehicle Speed Sensor &quot;A&quot; Intermittent / Erratic / High</dtcname><subpara id="RM100000000ZP8M_01" category="03"><name>DESCRIPTION</name><content5><ptxt>The skid control ECU (brake actuator assembly) outputs the vehicle speed signal to the ECM through the combination meter assembly.</ptxt><table type="dtc-explan-table" pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="4"><colspec colname="1" colwidth="0.71in"/><colspec colname="2" colwidth="0.71in"/><colspec colname="3" colwidth="3.89in"/><colspec colname="4" colwidth="1.77in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Detection Item</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC Detection Condition</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Trouble Area</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-code"><ptxt>P0503</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="detect-item"><ptxt>Vehicle Speed Sensor &quot;A&quot; Intermittent / Erratic / High</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-detect-cond"><ptxt>Cruise control in operation: When the ECM receives sudden changes in the vehicle speed signal</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="trouble-area"><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>Vehicle stability control system</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>Meter / gauge system</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>ECM</ptxt></item></list1></data-name></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000ZP8M_03" category="10"><name>CAUTION / NOTICE / HINT</name><content5><list1 type="unordered"><it